{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58375eca76","title":"给姜弘的一封信","origin":"《右派言论选集》（湖北人民出版社，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8502166d27","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"58375eca76"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f46655e252","name":"湖北"},{"id":"fa614e0916","name":"姚雪垠"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33ac3be5cb","type":"title","text":"给姜弘的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"7dde6fabdc","type":"authors","text":"湖北姚雪垠","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"195ee4f3a9","type":"paragraph","text":"[原编者按：这封信是从姚雪垠给姜弘的若干封信中选出来的一封。从这封信里已经明显地暴露了这批右派分子要使用一切手段，对党的领导，组织“里外夹攻”的恶毒企图。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"badff50670","type":"appellation","text":"姜弘：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"5424177482","type":"paragraph","text":"我的文章来不及写了，请你们不要等啦。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"6178b8a8b0","type":"paragraph","text":"接李蕤信，颇为振奋，我打算在赴北戴河之前写一文章，但不一定寄回《长文》发表。如交北京或上海发表，对武汉三大主义里外夹攻，力量也许大些。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"f6ef3a38d0","type":"paragraph","text":"几年来，武汉流行为生产服务理论以及如何压制反对者的事实，我不很清楚，请你写给我，以便言之有物。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"59f68b4cb3","type":"paragraph","text":"我在些（此）找的人日渐多起来，颇影响写作，故要提前去北戴河，离北京远一点。昨天我在中国书店专家服务部以10元高价买了一薄本旧书偶然遂，系一位明末襄城举人所写，叙述他被李自成队伍捕获及释放经过。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"a1b2df0f62","type":"paragraph","text":"关于程千帆与李尔重两同志，我已写一短文，交给“文汇报”了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"5b291dc1ca","type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！       雪垠","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"c012a7c2c6","type":"paragraph","text":" 6月8日","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"},{"id":"55eaa98661","type":"paragraph","text":"淑耘（作协武汉分会党组成员，长江文艺副主编——编者）如何打击李蕤及老宋（李蕤爱人“长江文艺”编辑——编者），也请详细写给我。希望在我动身前能收到你的信。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76"}],"page":{"id":"a03facc5dd","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58375eca76","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}